{"tid":890540,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"見得男/女朋友太多見到好想嘔xx(","createTime":"2018-11-05T11:37:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-06T09:26:07.000Z","uid":179026,"like":27,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a8c6e8010b175c95b72edbb6315b7bcf865ff7b5","tid":890540,"uid":179026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T11:37:18.000Z","msg":"熱戀中既情侶日見夜見都唔會厭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但拍拖耐咗<br />\n好似冇必要日夜都見<br />\n有啲人好似將佢既生活寄託咗係另一半身上<br />\n生活中既每一樣野都會聯繫到另一半<br />\n一揾唔到對方/對方唔揾佢<br />\n就會覺得冇野做<br />\n甚至覺得對方唔愛佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實咁樣既愛情非常幼稚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n每一個人都需要有自己既空間<br />\n你鐘意既興趣並唔代表對方都鐘意<br />\n你亦無需要迫自己去迎合對方<br />\n你想日日都見佢<br />\n有冇諗過對方想唔想？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好多情侶拍拖其實都玩到冇野好玩<br />\n好多時都係行街睇戲食飯扑野<br />\n或者只會留係屋企hea下<br />\n<br />\n有啲人會覺得<br />\n2個人一齊係到hea冇野做<br />\n但見到對方就好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得你要清楚對方係咪都鐘意咁做<br />\n因為有人其實會覺得：<br />\n冇野做出黎做咩/ 冇野做見黎做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而漸漸對見面產生反感<br />\n甚至會覺得好厭呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n適當既私人空間係一段感情中應有既元素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除非2條友都係同一類極煩既人<br />\n一定要日夜對住對方<br />\n唔見唔舒服<br />\n咁你地就真係唔需要私人空間了<br />\n但咁樣都只會係暫時<br />\n好快就會有其中一人因為見得多而厭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b62bdbc6bc37c50bbb4b7cab1f11d773b777a03f","tid":890540,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T11:38:29.000Z","msg":"作者經驗幾多？"},{"pid":"9d8a47bff037522e54e5125231a8a644ce48e9d0","tid":890540,"uid":52062,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T11:41:40.000Z","msg":"你咁講得, 只係證明到你同另一半期望同標準唔同,<br />\n有人中意日日見, 有人中意見少d, 冇話點先係最好<br />\n兩人都同意既方式, 先係最舒服既相處方式"},{"pid":"d14947e9c953990db3dbd45e0e258ced85a70693","tid":890540,"uid":20241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T11:46:18.000Z","msg":"你呢啲8婆真係好撚柒煩<br />\n見下有咩問題<br />\n小小野諸多不滿"},{"pid":"3181477e708b3c0f63ec2fb10ef2d2d3e8f2a542","tid":890540,"uid":179026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9d8a47bff037522e54e5125231a8a644ce48e9d0","tid":890540,"uid":52062,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T11:41:40.000Z","msg":"你咁講得, 只係證明到你同另一半期望同標準唔同,<br />\n有人中意日日見, 有人中意見少d, 冇話點先係最好<br />\n兩人都同意既方式, 先係最舒服既相處方式"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T12:02:22.000Z","msg":"同意呀 所以一定要清楚對方係咪鐘意你既模式"},{"pid":"64da4f3ba5804f3cc95b5db743cfa9ddabcdb71a","tid":890540,"uid":179026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d14947e9c953990db3dbd45e0e258ced85a70693","tid":890540,"uid":20241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T11:46:18.000Z","msg":"你呢啲8婆真係好撚柒煩<br />\n見下有咩問題<br />\n小小野諸多不滿"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T12:03:10.000Z","msg":"邊到見到我不滿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我又冇話見有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed904438a2ea9933c44c4f514b1ef340fa78199a","tid":890540,"uid":30710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T12:07:18.000Z","msg":"空間真係好緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3898a319a598a4426ca6de71b7bd114fb0ed2105","tid":890540,"uid":190657,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T19:56:48.000Z","msg":"見少啲對大家都好, 小別勝新婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da79d270bade381b7324743f7c694daebda1260d","tid":890540,"uid":162247,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":